Lindburgers Holding Company, LLC is committed to facilitating the accessibility and usability of its website, Lindburgers.com for all people with disabilities. Over time, as it is an intricate process, we will be working with a retained accessibility consultant concerning the relevant portions of The World Wide Web Consortiums Web Content Accessibility Guidelines 2.0 Level AA (WCAG 2.0 AA) as its web accessibility standard or other Standards to the extent required by the Americans with Disabilities Act (ADA).
